### User Registration
POST http://localhost:8090/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "payload": {
    "username": "testuser321",
    "password": "password321",
    "confirmPassword": "password321",
    "fullName": "Test User",
    "email": "testuser321@example.com",
    "phone": "1234567890",
    "type": 2
  }
}

###

### User Login
POST http://localhost:8090/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "payload": {
    "username": "testuser123",
    "password": "password123"
  }
}

###

### Create Category - Hotel
POST http://localhost:8090/api/category
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJzdWIiOiJ0ZXN0dXNlcjEyMyIsImlhdCI6MTc2MTU3NTgwNiwiZXhwIjoxNzYxNTc5NDA2fQ.6B2yJqSI4hYvy-yev-x0-RVo3zpVSy2oTBHff3mzIH0

{
  "payload": {
    "name": "Hotel",
    "type": "CATEGORY", 
    "description": "Comfortable hotel accommodations",
    "icon": "hotel_icon"
  }
}

